// The 'bpm' is the maximum pace, rather than an accurate average.
// The carrier frequency makes the background when beats are weak.
// Amplitude shaping adds a mild "ducking" effect, for drum pairs.
'bpm=480
'strength=100
Wsin f$strength/3 p[
	Rxpe mv f$bpm/120 a$strength*(240/$bpm)
] a1/2.r1[
	Rsqe mf f$bpm/120
] t30
